"4:43:47" : {s: 4, a: 43, w: 47, r: "عفو", t: "عَفُوًّا", l: "عَفُوّ", lc: 5, tl: "ʿafuwwan", lb: "ক্ষমা, মার্জনা",e: "Oft-Pardoning", b: "পাপমোচনকারী", i: "Maha Pemaaf", f: 3, rm: "to forgive/pardon, abound, pass over, forgo, grow, multiply, obliterate all traces, remit, give more than what is due, relinquish right or remit in whole or in part. afina (oblique pl. of afin) - forgiving. afuwwan - very forgiving, name of Allah. afwun - forgiveness, indulgence, surplus, superfluity. yafu - to pardon. ufiya - he is pardoned. (It does not necessarily imply the committing of a sin on the part of a person about whom it is used.)"},
